snippet.title: Rhyme Storm - 2020 Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Rhyme Storm is the world's first freestyle rapping rhythm game! It's packed with awesome beats, hilarious topics, and mind blowing visuals that dance and pulse to your performance. You won’t be asking if you can freestyle rap -- you’ll be wondering “how fast can I go?

Wishlist us on steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1250350/Rhyme_Storm/
Website: https://www.rhymestorm.com
facebook: https://www.facebook.com/rhymestormgame
twitter: https://www.twitter.com/rhyme_storm
